title: CRL Freshness
agents: active
catalog: agentless
license: GPL
distribution: https://github.com/jiuka/checkmk_crl_url

item:
 The name of the CRL given in the configuration.

description:
 This performs an active check of a CRL which is accessibale by http(s).

 It checks the publishing and expiration date of the CRL against the configured values.

 This check can be configured by Wato.